Docker - ThingsBoard PE installation Steps

run the following commands from terminal window one after other:

docker pull thingsboard/tb-pe:3.5.1PE

docker volume create mytbpe-data

docker volume create mytbpe-data-db

docker volume create mytbpe-logs

docker compose up -d

docker compose logs -f mytbpe

After completion of Things Board Installation:

Execute: http://localhost:8080

You should see ThingsBoard login page. Use the following default credentials:

Tenant Administrator: tenant@thingsboard.org / tenant
